T02D3348:34a-1: autstshu sma dzam bha la s'a dha nam /
T02D3348:34a-3: autstshusma dzam bha la'i sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02D3348:34a-4: bcom ldan 'das dzam bha la la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3348:34a-5: aom a'a:zhes bya bas phab ste /
T02D3348:34a-6: rang gi snying gar aa yongs su gyur pa las
T02D3348:34a-7: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su h'um las rdo
T02D3348:34a-8: rje rtse dgu pa'i dbus su dbang po sbas pa
T02D3348:34a-10: sngon du bstan pa 'bebs pa'i sngags kyis phab la /
T02D3348:34a-11: dzam bha la mgon po rang gi snying gar rab tu bcug pas /
T02D3348:34a-12: autstshusma mi'u thung gi gzugs rna ba ma phug pa mdog nag pa /
T02D3348:34a-13: skra kham pa gyen du bsgreng ba /
T02D3348:34a-14: lus thung bar byed cing khro gnyer can /
T02D3348:34a-15: mche ba dang ldan pa rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dbu rgyan can /
T02D3348:34a-16: klu chen po brgyad kyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa'i g-yon
T02D3348:34a-17: pa'i phyag na rin po che la sogs pa skyugs
T02D3348:34a-19: g-yas na khrag gis bkang ba'i thod pa bsnams pa'o //
T02D3348:34a-20: mgo g-yas phyogs su bstan pa'i gser gyi mdog can /
T02D3348:34a-21: rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa'i nor sbyin 'gyel ba
T02D3348:34a-22: la zhabs gnyis kyis mnan pas rin po che'i snyem
T02D3348:34a-23: la sogs pa skyugs par byed pa'o //
T02D3348:34a-24: 'od 'phro ba'i phreng ba 'khrigs pa'i bdag nyid du bsams la /
T02D3348:34a-25: autstshusma'i g-yas pa'i phyag tu aam las skyes pa gru gsum pa sa ka ta bsam mo //
T02D3348:34b-0: bam las skyes pa'i bum @34b ba bzang po 'bo bzhin pa'o //
T02D3348:34b-1: lag pa'i dbus su dzam ngo //
T02D3348:34b-8: de nas sv'a h'a zhes pa ni logs gnyis la'o //
T02D3348:34b-9: sngags dgod pa bsgom pa'i rim pa'o /
T02D3348:34b-10: kha mngon par bsngags la chu sbyin sbyin par bya'o //
T02D3348:34b-12: chu khyor ba nas sbyin pa'i sngags so //
T02D3348:34b-13: aom aindra ni mu kham bhra ma ri sv'a h'a /
T02D3348:34b-16: de nas zhal du sbyin par bya'o //
T02D3348:34b-17: de ltar snying rjes sems can dbul ba'i sdug bsngal
T02D3348:34b-18: bcad pa'i don du dzam bha la bsgom pa ni
T02D3348:34b-19: dzam bha la nyid du 'gyur ro //
T02D3348:34b-20: autstshusma dzam bha la'i sgrub pa'i thabs rnal 'byor pa dga' ba sbyin gyis mdzad pa rdzogs so //
T02D3348:34b-21: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
